{"CHISEL":[{"def":"A tool with a cutting edge on one end of a metal blade, used in dressing, shaping, or working in timber, stone, metal, etc.","pos":""}],"CHISLEU":[{"def":"The ninth month of the Jewish ecclesiastical year, answering to a part of November with a part of December.","pos":""}],"CHISLEY":[{"def":"Having a large admixture of small pebbles or gravel; -- said of a soil.","pos":""}]}